Text.val: This variabele always contains the date the cursor is currently on.
This block is executed when the engine is in backward mode, going to
Variables for date grid. The cursor is allowed to park on the field
that corresponds to the date v:Working date only.
We get to this block when the engine is executing in forward mode,
Initialise working variable v:Date to parameter date if supplied, else
Skip to next year upon action 'End Table'
Skip to previous year upon action 'Begin Table'
Skip to next month upon action 'Next Screen'
Skip to previous month upon action 'Previous Screen'
